<div class="container py-5">
  <div class="row justify-content-center">
    <div class="col-lg-6">
      <div class="card border-danger">
        <div class="card-body text-center py-5">
          <div class="mb-4">
            <i class="bi bi-x-circle-fill text-danger" style="font-size: 4rem;"></i>
          </div>
          <h1 class="text-danger mb-3">Pago fallido</h1>
          <p class="lead mb-4">No pudimos procesar el pago de tu reserva.</p>
          <div class="bg-light rounded p-4 mb-4">
            <h5 class="mb-3">Detalles de la reserva</h5>
            <p class="mb-1"><strong>Reserva:</strong> #<%= @booking.id %></p>
            <p class="mb-1"><strong>Mentor:</strong> <%= @booking.availability.mentor.full_name %></p>
            <p class="mb-1"><strong>Fecha:</strong> <%= I18n.l(@booking.starts_at, format: :long) %></p>
            <p class="mb-0"><strong>Monto:</strong> $<%= number_with_precision(@booking.price, precision: 2) %></p>
          </div>
          <div class="alert alert-warning text-start" role="alert">
            <strong>¿Qué puedes hacer?</strong>
            <ul class="mb-0 mt-2">
              <li>Llorar porque a veces las cosas no salen como esperamos</li>
              <li>Salir a dar un paseo paraa tocar pasto</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="d-grid gap-2">
            <%= button_to "Reintentar pago", checkout_students_booking_path(@booking), method: :post, class: "btn btn-danger btn-lg", data: { turbo: false } %>
            <%= link_to "Ver detalles de la reserva", students_booking_path(@booking), class: "btn btn-outline-secondary" %>
            <%= link_to "Volver a mis reservas", students_bookings_path, class: "btn btn-outline-secondary" %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>